operator.title: Check STD for LVH
operator.synopsis: Super Operator Template for Check STD for LVH

text.paragraph: This is a super operator defined for Check STD for LVH in ECG diagnosis, with pre-deined input ports and outpot ports.
The input Model port receives the step model.

inputPorts.port: Input port for the step model. This operator will add its inner process to this step.
